    "Html": "Hi, <br>\r\ni need to create a new style based on NBR 10520 [<a href=\"http://www.unerj.br/unerj/pesquisa/arquivos/CITACOES_NBR10520.pdf\">http://www.unerj.br/unerj/pesquisa/arquivos/CITACOES_NBR10520.pdf</a>] ( Brazillian Standard) for using on my dissertation. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSamples of citation :&nbsp;<br>\r\ni)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Times New Roman\">(CAGLIARI e RIZZO, 1989).<br>\r\n</span>ii)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Times New Roman\">(SHILINGBURG; HOBO; WHISETT, 1983).</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nI´m trying to use BibWord. So, i´ve already copy BibWordStyleSheet.xsl to &lt;C:\\Arquivos de programas\\Microsoft Office\\Office12\\Bibliography\\Style&gt; and all styles available on site. <br>\r\nBut i´m a little bit confuse how to proceed. <br>\r\nWhere i can get more information about this? <br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks for any help.\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2008-10-16T11:17:03.907-07:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
